        "TileImage": "$($repository f65fff84-6cad-4a11-9a0a-b89430c03397).Image",
        "Description": "47 has been contracted to eliminate Jordan Cross, the lead singer of popular rock band The Class, and the son of multimillionaire media mogul Thomas Cross.\r\rOne year ago, Jordan murdered Hannah Highmoore during an argument. Jordan evaded prosecution thanks to his father&apos;s influence and a legal defense by the family&apos;s lawyer, Ken Morgan. Seeking retribution, the Highmoore family has asked the ICA to eliminate both Jordan and Morgan.\r\rInfiltrate the Himmapan Hotel and eliminate both targets.",
